headline: A Look At Public Service Enterprise Group (PEG) Valuation After Recent Share Price Moves
summary: Public Service Enterprise Group (PEG) is drawing attention after recent share price moves, with the stock closing at $81.18 as investors weigh its utility operations, nuclear generation exposure and recent return profile. See our latest analysis for Public Service Enterprise Group.
